      ],
      "source": "https://www.longportlibrary.njlibraries.org/?view=article&id=17:history-of-longport&catid=9"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Longport sits on the southern tip of Absecon Island, a barrier island on New Jersey’s coast.",
